<bibRefCitation author="Papp, L. &amp; Cerny, M." box="[520,760,1592,1619]" pageId="23" pageNumber="476" refId="ref19613" refString="Papp, L. &amp; Cerny, M. 2015. Agromyzidae (Diptera) of Hungary. Volume 1. Agromyzinae. Nagykovacsi, Pars Ltd., 1 - 416. DOI: http: // doi. org / 10.18655 / Agromyzidae. Vol. 1." type="book" year="2015">Papp &amp; Černý, 2015</bibRefCitation>
