<bibRefCitation author="Guglya, Yu." pageId="23" pageNumber="476" pagination="61 - 68" refId="ref19059" refString="Guglya, Yu. 2011. A study of the fauna of leaf-miner flies of the subfamily Agromyzinae (Diptera: Agromyzidae) of Ukraine. Report 1. 28 new species for the fauna of Ukraine. The Kharkov Entomological Society Gazette, 19 (2), 61 - 68 [In Russian]." type="journal article" year="2011">Guglya, 2011</bibRefCitation>
